  "description": "Product Description Mini Robot Toy Interactive Sensory Play The walking and talking interactive robot toy is the perfect playtime companion for children aged six months and over, with twistable, posable limbs, lights, sounds and eyes that revolve; the robot offers all kinds of sensory play fun to aid in early development. When seated, the robot can even roll along the floor thanks to the wheels built into the back of its legs! Lights &amp; Sounds Flashing lights and sounds paired with large buttons, movable limbs and even revolving eyes make the Mini Robot a tactile, sensory toy perfect for developing hand eye coordination as well as providing key auditory and visual stimulation for early years development Auto Shut Off Made of non-toxic plastics, the Mini Robot has been tested to UK CE standards, and comes with batteries included. The built in automatic shut off system allows the mini robot to conserve its battery life - so it won't keep going even if little ones forget to turn it off! Suitable for 6 + Months Geared up and ready to play right out of the box, this interactive robot toy is designed with little ones in mind with lots of cool interactive features and moving parts to discover, paired with a cute, chunky design easy for small hands to grab and hold.",
